text: See also: Hengelo, Overijssel \---- Hengelo (Achterhooks: Hengel) is a town in the province of Gelderland, the Netherlands. 7,995 people are living there in 2022.AlleCijfers.nl Hengelo lies in the Achterhoek region, and is the main seat of the municipality of Bronckhorst. It was a municipality of its own until 2005. ==Born== * Annemarie Jorritsma, politician ==References== Category:Settlements in Gelderland Category:Former municipalities of Gelderland Category:Achterhoek
